summary: Greg Andersen calls Julie D'Arcane to ask for help with his hacky sacks. The sacks have been up on the balcony since 1988.
suggested_actions: Confirm the exact time of Greg Andersen's visit to retrieve the hacky sacks.
Ensure that the hacky sacks are accessible and ready for pickup on the balcony.
Follow up with Greg after the visit to ensure he successfully retrieved the items and address any further needs.
